### S0/tests/fixtures/http_admin.http — shablon zaprosov dlya VS Code REST Client
# Mosty:
# - Yavnyy: Enderton (logika) — proveryaemye predikaty zaprosov (GET /admin c/bez tokena).
# - Skrytyy #1: Ashbi (kibernetika) — minimalnyy regulyator: dva zaprosa dostatochno dlya bazovoy diagnostiki.
# - Skrytyy #2: Cover & Thomas — minimalnyy «signal» dlya razlicheniya sostoyaniy RBAC.
# Zemnoy abzats (inzheneriya): ruchnoy smouk bez instrumentov — udobno pri lokalnoy gonke.
# c=a+b

@base = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@jwt  = {{jwt}}   # podstav syuda token ili ispolzuy peremennye REST Client

### /live
GET {{base}}/live

### /ready
GET {{base}}/ready

### /admin bez tokena (ozhidaetsya 401/403/302)
GET {{base}}/admin

### /admin s tokenom (ozhidaetsya 200/302)
GET {{base}}/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
